FLIGHT SIM 2 - KEYBOARD COMMANDS

Docs typed by Nasty Boy & Pandora.
 
         
MAIN KEYBOARD COMMANDS


F2  - Toggle 3D view on/off
F3  - Toggle Map on/off
F9  - Zoom In
F10 - Zoom Out

9   - E.T up
0   - E.T down

Q   - Save game
W   - Load game
E   - Load extra scenery etc...
R   - Left Front view
T   - Cockpit view 
Y   - Right Front view
U   - Toggle gear on/off
I   - Toggle Cabheater on/off
O   - Toggle shadow light/dark
P   - Pause
[   - Open flaps
]   - Close flaps
A   - Load saved flight
S   - External view
D   - Tracker
F   - Left view
G   - Ground view
H   - Right view
L   - Toggle lights on/off
N   - Right Back view
B   - Back view
V   - Left Back view
C   - Control Tower view


NUMERIC KEYPAD

1   - Brake
2   - Lift Nose
3   - Throttle down
4   - Plane left
6   - Plane right
8   - Lower Nose
9   - Throttle up

CURSOR KEYS - Numerous external views.

Click at top of screen for menus.



End.
